My LA peeps, if you haven’t seen Les Mis at The Pantages… don’t miss @nickcartell as Jean Valjean. I met Nick when I was 9 years old… we did “The Sound of Music” and “The Secret Garden” together. (That’s us in the picture.) I adored him… and still do. Let’s just say, I ugly cried through the whole show last night. Bravo, Nick! 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻

Happy birthday, @welcometoheidi! My adventure buddy, my fashion inspiration and friend who offers to pick me up at LAX…you’re one of a kind and I am so lucky to know you. May this be your best year yet! I love, love, love you!
Happy birthday, soul sister! Love, love, love you.
